        而是教育机构的<strong>操作系统</strong><br>
        从教师到学生，从课堂到家庭，从内容到数据<br>
        端到端打通。
      </span>
      <span data-lang-en class="block">
        Not another AI tool.<br>
        The <strong>operating system</strong> for education<br>
        from teachers to students, classroom to home<br>
        content to data, end-to-end.
      </span>
