<!-- ===== ARCHITECTURE ===== -->
<section id="architecture">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="eyebrow fade-up"><span data-lang-zh>技术架构</span><span data-lang-en>Architecture</span></span>
    <h2 class="fade-up"><span data-lang-zh>DynamOS 系统架构</span><span data-lang-en>DynamOS System Architecture</span></h2>
    <p class="fade-up"><span data-lang-zh>四层架构：接入层、应用层、引擎层、数据层。</span><span data-lang-en>Four-layer architecture: Access, Application, Engine, Data.</span></p>
  </div>

  <div class="arch-section">
    <div class="arch-diagram">
      <div class="arch-layer fade-up">
        <h4>🔌 <span data-lang-zh>接入层</span><span data-lang-en>Access Layer</span></h4>
        <ul>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>教师 Web 仪表盘</span><span data-lang-en>Teacher Web Dashboard</span></li>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>学生移动端 (iOS/Android PWA)</span><span data-lang-en>Student Mobile (iOS/Android PWA)</span></li>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>家长微信小程序</span><span data-lang-en>Parent WeChat Mini Program</span></li>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>机构管理后台</span><span data-lang-en>School Admin Panel</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="arch-layer fade-up">
        <h4>🧩 <span data-lang-zh>应用层</span><span data-lang-en>Application Layer</span></h4>
        <ul>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>DynaDict · 智能词典</span><span data-lang-en>DynaDict · Smart Dictionary</span></li>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>DynaSpeak · AI 口语教练</span><span data-lang-en>DynaSpeak · AI Speaking Coach</span></li>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>DynaWrite · 写作批改引擎</span><span data-lang-en>DynaWrite · Writing Correction Engine</span></li>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>DynaTrack · 进度追踪系统</span><span data-lang-en>DynaTrack · Progress Tracking System</span></li>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>DynaPlan · 智能排课引擎</span><span data-lang-en>DynaPlan · Smart Scheduling Engine</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="arch-layer fade-up">
        <h4>⚙️ <span data-lang-zh>引擎层</span><span data-lang-en>Engine Layer</span></h4>
        <ul>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>内容生成引擎 (教学法约束)</span><span data-lang-en>Content Engine (Pedagogy-Guarded)</span></li>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>自适应难度引擎 (i+1)</span><span data-lang-en>Adaptive Difficulty Engine (i+1)</span></li>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>间隔重复引擎</span><span data-lang-en>Spaced Repetition Engine</span></li>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>语音评测引擎</span><span data-lang-en>Pronunciation Assessment Engine</span></li>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>学习分析引擎 (40+ 维度)</span><span data-lang-en>Learning Analytics Engine (40+ dims)</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="arch-layer fade-up">
        <h4>💾 <span data-lang-zh>数据层</span><span data-lang-en>Data Layer</span></h4>
        <ul>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>学生能力图谱 (知识追踪)</span><span data-lang-en>Student Competency Map (Knowledge Tracing)</span></li>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>机构内容库 (多租户隔离)</span><span data-lang-en>School Content Library (Multi-Tenant)</span></li>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>教学策略库 (RUA 框架)</span><span data-lang-en>Pedagogy Strategy DB (RUA Framework)</span></li>
          <li><span data-lang-zh>合规日志 (数据主权保证)</span><span data-lang-en>Compliance Logs (Data Sovereignty)</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== MOAT — Bento Grid ===== -->
<section id="moat">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="eyebrow fade-up"><span data-lang-zh>竞争壁垒</span><span data-lang-en>Competitive Moat</span></span>
    <h2 class="fade-up"><span data-lang-zh>为什么是 DynamOS</span><span data-lang-en>Why DynamOS</span></h2>
    <p class="fade-up"><span data-lang-zh>不是又一个 AI 噱头。这是六个真正的壁垒。</span><span data-lang-en>Not another AI gimmick. Six real moats.</span></p>
  </div>

  <div class="moat-bento">
    <!-- Moat 1: Pedagogy-First — Wide -->
    <div class="moat-card moat-wide fade-up">
      <span class="moat-icon">🧠</span>
      <h4><span data-lang-zh>教学法先行</span><span data-lang-en>Pedagogy-First</span></h4>
      <p><span data-lang-zh>不是"AI 很强所以我们用 AI"。而是"这些教学法有效，我们用 AI 来实现它们"。每个功能背后都有教育学论文支持。</span><span data-lang-en>Not "AI is powerful so let's use AI." It's "these pedagogies work, let's implement them with AI." Every feature backed by research.</span></p>
    </div>

    <!-- Moat 2: System Not Tools -->
    <div class="moat-card fade-up">
      <span class="moat-icon">🏗️</span>
      <h4><span data-lang-zh>系统而非工具</span><span data-lang-en>System, Not Tools</span></h4>
      <p><span data-lang-zh>竞品给你一个 AI 出题器、一个批改工具。DynamOS 给你一个完整系统 —— 教师端、学生端、家长端、内容引擎和数据分析全部互通。</span><span data-lang-en>Competitors give you an AI quiz generator or an essay corrector. DynamOS gives you a complete system — teacher, student, parent, content, and analytics all connected.</span></p>
    </div>

    <!-- Moat 3: Chinese Learner-First -->
    <div class="moat-card fade-up">
      <span class="moat-icon">🇨🇳</span>
      <h4><span data-lang-zh>中国学习者定制</span><span data-lang-en>Chinese Learner-First</span></h4>
      <p><span data-lang-zh>不为"通用学习者"设计。中英对比分析、母语迁移干预、RUA 循环 —— 所有设计基于中国学习者的真实认知过程。</span><span data-lang-en>Not designed for "generic learners." Chinese-English contrastive analysis, L1 transfer intervention, RUA cycle — all based on how Chinese learners actually think.</span></p>
    </div>

    <!-- Moat 4: Data Sovereignty -->
    <div class="moat-card fade-up">
      <span class="moat-icon">🔒</span>
      <h4><span data-lang-zh>数据主权 &amp; 内容溯源</span><span data-lang-en>Data Sovereignty &amp; Traceability</span></h4>
      <p><span data-lang-zh>机构数据本地化部署选项。每道内容可溯源到其教育学设计决策。不是"相信 AI" —— 而是"理解 AI"。</span><span data-lang-en>On-premise deployment option for school data. Every piece of content traceable to its pedagogical design decisions. Not "trust the AI" — "understand the AI."</span></p>
    </div>

    <!-- Moat 5: Anti-Slop Content -->
    <div class="moat-card fade-up">
      <span class="moat-icon">📚</span>
      <h4><span data-lang-zh>去"AI 味"内容</span><span data-lang-en>Anti-Slop Content</span></h4>
      <p><span data-lang-zh>LLM 直接输出的内容一眼就能看出来 —— 重复、空洞、缺乏教学结构。DynamOS 的内容引擎输出像资深老师手写的教材。</span><span data-lang-en>LLM-direct output is instantly recognizable — repetitive, hollow, no pedagogical structure. DynamOS content reads like a textbook hand-written by a veteran teacher.</span></p>
    </div>

    <!-- Moat 6: Retention-Friendly — Wide -->
    <div class="moat-card moat-wide fade-up">
      <span class="moat-icon">📈</span>
      <h4><span data-lang-zh>续费友好设计</span><span data-lang-en>Retention-Friendly Design</span></h4>
      <p><span data-lang-zh>家长能看到真实进步，学生有成就感和技能树，教师减少重复劳动。三个角色都受益 = 续费率提升。这不是承诺，是系统架构的自然结果。</span><span data-lang-en>Parents see real progress, students get achievement and skill trees, teachers reduce drudgery. All three roles win = retention rises. Not a promise — a natural consequence of the system architecture.</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

