        <div class="phase-sub"><span data-lang-zh>第 3-5 个月</span><span data-lang-en>Months 3-5</span></div>
        <h4><span data-lang-zh>🔄 迭代</span><span data-lang-en>🔄 Iterate</span></h4>
        <p><span data-lang-zh>扩展到5-10个班级，上线课辅端+进度追踪器。验证家长满意度、续费指标改善。建立标杆案例。</span><span data-lang-en>Scale to 5-10 classes, launch Parent Hub + Progress Tracker. Validate parent satisfaction and retention improvement. Build reference cases.</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="phase fade-up">
