        <h4><span data-lang-zh>🚀 规模化</span><span data-lang-en>🚀 Scale</span></h4>
        <p><span data-lang-zh>全校部署，内容引擎全面启用。多机构支持。数据驱动续费预测。成型方法论可复制到其他机构。</span><span data-lang-en>Full-school deployment, Content Engine fully online. Multi-school support. Data-driven retention prediction. Replicable methodology for other schools.</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

